name: First Edition - Six Pack
description: Love you some Craft Beer Cards? Have craft beer friends who need to get a taste? This taster tray comes with 6 of the normal 5-packs, so you'll get 30 cards at a discounted price. You'll also have a solid chance at getting all 12 of the first edition cards. Odds are good.

name: First Edition Pack
description:
Pack of 5 cards from the limited first edition print of trading cards. All trading cards printed on thick stock kraft paper, full-color front, b/w back. Designs, illustrations, printing, and packaging all produced in Portland, Oregon, USA.

Each pack contains a random set of 5 trading cards from the first edition of Craft Beer Cards, sealed along with a first edition logo card, listing all 12 collectible cards in the first edition.
